        {
          "name": "places/ChIJa7zfoiDLRIYR1Sb-iOrB62E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNU5ESkNXbTh6T1dkcFNYRnhNek5LZWpjMmNuYxAB",
          "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago",
          "rating": 4,
          "text": {
            "text": "The variety of drinks is good, and the drink flavors are pretty solid. The staff is nice. This place used to be a different boba shop, and I didn’t notice any major improvements to the interior—hence my 3-star rating for atmosphere.",
