          "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNU5ESkNXbTh6T1dkcFNYRnhNek5LZWpjMmNuYxAB!2m1!1s0x8644cb20a2dfbc6b:0x61ebc1ea88fe26d5"
        },
        {
          "name": "places/ChIJa7zfoiDLRIYR1Sb-iOrB62E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWGNqRlliRE5MYmtSRVFXbFVkWHByUzA5NExYYxAB",
          "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago",
          "rating": 5,
          "text": {
            "text": "Their soft opening week was very busy! It took about 45 minutes waiting in line to get drinks. We ordered Vietnamese coffee and a pistachio latte. Both were delicious! They did a good job redecorating the interior and making the seating area cozy. It's great to see a new coffee shop getting lots of business, but I'd strongly recommend going during their non busy hours if you're looking to just grab a coffee and go.",
            "languageCode": "en"
          },
          "originalText": {
            "text": "Their soft opening week was very busy! It took about 45 minutes waiting in line to get drinks. We ordered Vietnamese coffee and a pistachio latte. Both were delicious! They did a good job redecorating the interior and making the seating area cozy. It's great to see a new coffee shop getting lots of business, but I'd strongly recommend going during their non busy hours if you're looking to just grab a coffee and go.",
            "languageCode": "en"
          },
