          "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psUlZHVkdVV1YzU21oWFpqVlZVbVJXYTBsVVNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x8644cb20a2dfbc6b:0x61ebc1ea88fe26d5"
        },
        {
          "name": "places/ChIJa7zfoiDLRIYR1Sb-iOrB62E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psMVFUQlFkMVYyZUV0NlEzZDNUMFJTVFc1cmVVRRAB",
          "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago",
          "rating": 5,
          "text": {
            "text": "I recently visited Dâm Coffee Bar because I have been a little obsessed with oat milk matcha with a pump of vanilla, and I am on the hunt for the best one in Austin. This spot simply won me over. The place is beautiful, very calm, and comfortable to work from, and the matcha was absolutely divine. The service could be better, but overall I really enjoyed my visit. Definitely coming back!",
            "languageCode": "en"
          },
          "originalText": {
            "text": "I recently visited Dâm Coffee Bar because I have been a little obsessed with oat milk matcha with a pump of vanilla, and I am on the hunt for the best one in Austin. This spot simply won me over. The place is beautiful, very calm, and comfortable to work from, and the matcha was absolutely divine. The service could be better, but overall I really enjoyed my visit. Definitely coming back!",
            "languageCode": "en"
