          "rating": 5,
          "text": {
            "text": "I stopped by ĐẬM Coffee Bar during their soft opening and was blown away! The space has such a cool, industrial-urban vibe — perfect for studying, working, or just hanging out with friends.\n\nI tried their iced matcha latte and it was incredible — smooth, perfectly balanced, and not too sweet. You can really taste the quality of their ingredients. The baristas were friendly, fast, and clearly passionate about what they do.\n\nIt’s such a great addition to the neighborhood, and I can already tell this will be my go-to spot for coffee and matcha. Highly recommend checking it out!",
            "languageCode": "en"
          },
          "originalText": {
